{
  "stem": "10644.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A doctor, you know, maybe, you know, maybe the, the-- yes, for sure, you know, it was some, some respect in this-- in-- from this point of view.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- I-- with the same Volkswagen I was brought to the hospital in Siedlce.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was told, you have to stay there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Stay there.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I got my, my small room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I started to work with wounded soldiers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, Polish soldiers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Germans, they were not allowed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was only Polish soldiers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was in the city hospital of Siedlce.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Shortly, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there was-- Siedlce was, at the beginning, was occupied by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then, you know, somehow on agreement with Russia, Siedlce has to belong to the Russians.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So suddenly, the Germans moving out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they say to all doctors, personnel who wants to go to the west can go with us to the west.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And who wants to stay, will stay.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I stayed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And here the Russians came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But after four days, was already again a change.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The, the Germans are coming again to Siedlce.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So there was a question of whether River Bug or River Wisla is a border.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It is-- they didn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, [? because I informed ?] the-- they are coming.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, went to the director, I say, please, we have-- there were several hundred wounded.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From this several hundred, now we have around 30, 40, 40-- we-- enough still doctors.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Can I leave?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he say, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You can leave.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he allowed me to leave and to go to Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Bialystok was in the Russian hands.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I went to Bialystok, Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My, my, my my, parents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- I stayed in, in Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
